### ============================================================
### USER MANAGEMENT API REQUESTS
### Web Admins, Officers, and Agents
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================
### WEB ADMINS (Requires web_admin role)
### ============================================================

### Get all web admins
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/web-admins
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Web admins fetched successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "admins": [
#             {
#                 "id": 1,
#                 "admin_level": "super_admin",
#                 "title": "System Administrator",
#                 "user": {
#                     "id": 1,
#                     "name": "Admin User",
#                     "email": "admin@constituency.gov.gh",
#                     "status": "active"
#                 }
#             }
#         ]
#     }
# }

###

### Get single web admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/web-admins/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create new web admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/web-admins
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "name": "New Admin",
    "email": "newadmin@constituency.gov.gh",
    "phone": "+233249973054",
    "admin_level": "admin",
    "title": "Content Manager",
    "permissions": ["manage_blog", "manage_events", "manage_faqs"]
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Web admin created successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "admin": {...},
#         "generated_password": "Xp9#kL2mN@"
#     }
# }

###

### Update web admin
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/web-admins/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "admin_level": "moderator",
    "permissions": ["manage_blog"]
}

###

### Delete web admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/web-admins/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### ============================================================
### OFFICERS (Requires web_admin role)
### ============================================================

