### ============================================================
### AGENTS (Requires web_admin or officer role)
### ============================================================

### Get all agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/agents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get single agent
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/agents/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create new agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/agents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "name": "Ama Serwah",
    "email": "ama@agents.constituency.gov.gh",
    "phone": "+233249973056",
    "supervisor_id": 1,
    "assigned_communities": ["Village A", "Village B", "Town C"],
    "id_type": "Ghana Card",
    "id_number": "GHA-XXXXXXXXXX-X"
}

